" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 30, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rdo1665702649920.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rdo1665702649920.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rdo1665702649920.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rdo1665702649920\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n uOleContainer (OleContainer)\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uOleContainer</code> widget displays an embedded OLE object, enabling you to define links to OLE objects in Uniface applications.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__section_qd5_q4p_fcc\">\n<p class=\"p\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"akm1704707836734.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/akm1704707836734.html\" title=\"By default, Uniface displays most fields as edit boxes, but you can change this by selecting a different widget and optionally setting its widget properties. You can do this at the model level, for example in modeled entities or modeled components, or you can do this in the components themselves.\">Specifying a Widget for a Field or Entity</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__section_w1004ab1b5b3_w1005ab1b5_w1006ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d708931e67\">\n                       \n Widget Properties\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">OLE Container Widget Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Property</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Technical Name</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"txj1665702628158.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/txj1665702628158.html\" title=\"This property determines whether a three-dimensional appearance is applied when the widget is displayed. True (default) or False.\">3-D Effect (3d)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">3D</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fvi1665702649989.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fvi1665702649989.html\" title=\"Comma-separated list of object classes that can be held in the OLE container widget. Default value is All (all types of OLE objects are allowed in the OLE container).\">Allowed Classes</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">AllowedClass</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jjb1665702650062.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jjb1665702650062.html\" title=\"Determines whether the widget can contain an embedded object. True (default) or False.\">Allow Embedded Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">AllowEmbedding</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gpj1665702650132.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gpj1665702650132.html\" title=\"Determines whether the widget can be linked to an object. True (default) or False\">Allow Linked Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">AllowLink</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bou1665702610816.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bou1665702610816.html\" title=\"The Attach to Window Border (Attach) widget property attaches the widget (or area frame) to one or more form window borders or split bars at runtime. This allows the element to be resized or moved when the window is resized or a split bar moved.\">Attach to Window Border (attach)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Attach</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwc1665702587483.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwc1665702587483.html\" title=\"Color to use as the background of the object.\">Background Color (BackColor)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">BackColor</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xfh1665702650201.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfh1665702650201.html\" title=\"Indicates whether the widget displays an icon or the data itself.\">Display as Icon</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">DisplayAsIcon</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"anr1665702650271.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/anr1665702650271.html\" title=\"Determines whether the valueChanged trigger is executed when linked data in the OLE container is changed. True or False (default).\">NotifyOnChange</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">NotifyOnChange</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"svg1665702629592.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svg1665702629592.html\" title=\"Determines whether a border is displayed around the widget at run time. True or False. The default value depends on the widget.\">Frame</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Frame</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mdg1665702628370.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mdg1665702628370.html\" title=\"Font for the label associated with this widget. The specified label font is also used in widgets that support tool tip text. If not specified, the font definition in the application's .ini file is used.\">Label Font ( LabelFont)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">LabelFont</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fwg1665702644164.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fwg1665702644164.html\" title=\"Specify the mouse action that activates the valueChanged trigger\">Mouse Activation (MouseActivation)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">MouseActivation</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kml1665702613321.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kml1665702613321.html\" title=\"Size of the margin in pixels, on all sides of the widget, when it is attached to at least one window border. The value can be the number of pixels (for example, 2px) or classic.\">Attach Margin (AttachMargin)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">AttachMargin</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qff1665702581606.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qff1665702581606.html\" title=\"Defines the position and size of a rectangle to use as an anchor for a popup form, in character cells or pixels. The default value is 0,0,0,0.\">Popup Rectangle (PopupRect)</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">PopupRect</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rdo1665702649920__table_d13502e1_d13503e1_d13504e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__section_w1007ab1b5b5_w1008ab1b5_w1009ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d708931e525\">\n                       \n Triggers\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__d6865e22\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bqj1665702585000.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bqj1665702585000.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to an interactive event on a field or entity widget, such as the user clicking on the field.\">trigger detail</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__d6865e27\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kke1665702605570.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kke1665702605570.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger for that determines what happens after a user changes the value of a field in a form component.\">trigger valueChanged</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__section_w1010ab1b5b7_w1011ab1b5_w1012ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d708931e554\">\n                       \n Default Logical Widget\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__p_d113330e1_d113331e1_d113332e1\">Uniface provides a logical widget called OleContainer, which is mapped to <code class=\"ph codeph\">uOleContainer</code>:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__p_d113333e1_d113334e1_d113335e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">OcxContainer=uOcxContainer</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__section_w1013ab1b5b9_w1014ab1b5_w1015ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d708931e572\">\n                       \n Grid and MSAA Support\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__d6541e20\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Supports MSAA? :</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__section_w1016ab1b5c11_w1017ab1b5_w1018ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d708931e610\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__p_d113342e1_d113343e1_d113344e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uOleContainer</code> widget allows you to embed or define links to Object Linking and Embedding (OLE) objects in your Uniface applications. The <code class=\"ph codeph\">uOleContainer</code> can contain only one embedded or linked OLE object, although you can have more than one <code class=\"ph codeph\">uOleContainer</code> on a form. This widget allows you to integrate OLE objects (such as audio files, Microsoft Excel spreadsheets, and so on) into Uniface applications.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__p_d113345e1_d113346e1_d113347e1\">This widget is available only for Microsoft Windows 2000 and higher.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__p_d113348e1_d113349e1_d113350e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">UOLEINSERTOBJECT</code> function allows you to access the OLE pointer held in Uniface. This function must be exported as follows:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">XEXPORT (void) UOLEINSERTOBJECT (void)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rdo1665702649920__p_d113351e1_d113352e1_d113353e1\">If the user focuses on the <code class=\"ph codeph\">uOleContainer</code>, by pressing either GOLD D or Control+D, the Detail trigger is activated.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531544\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531544\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "uOleContainer (OleContainer) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 30, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 uOleContainer (OleContainer) The uOleContainer widget displays an embedded OLE object, enabling you to define links to OLE objects in Uniface applications. For more information, see Specifying a Widget for a Field or Entity . Widget Properties Table 1. OLE Container Widget Properties Property Technical Name Dynamic? 3-D Effect (3d) 3D Yes Allowed Classes AllowedClass No Allow Embedded Object AllowEmbedding Yes Allow Linked Object AllowLink Yes Attach to Window Border (attach) Attach Yes Background Color (BackColor) BackColor Yes Display as Icon DisplayAsIcon Yes NotifyOnChange NotifyOnChange Frame Frame Yes Label Font ( LabelFont) LabelFont Yes Mouse Activation (MouseActivation) MouseActivation Yes Attach Margin (AttachMargin) AttachMargin Yes Popup Rectangle (PopupRect) PopupRect Yes Triggers trigger detail trigger valueChanged Default Logical Widget Uniface provides a logical widget called OleContainer, which is mapped to uOleContainer : OcxContainer=uOcxContainer Grid and MSAA Support Supported in Grid? No Supports MSAA? : No Description The uOleContainer widget allows you to embed or define links to Object Linking and Embedding (OLE) objects in your Uniface applications. The uOleContainer can contain only one embedded or linked OLE object, although you can have more than one uOleContainer on a form. This widget allows you to integrate OLE objects (such as audio files, Microsoft Excel spreadsheets, and so on) into Uniface applications. This widget is available only for Microsoft Windows 2000 and higher. The UOLEINSERTOBJECT function allows you to access the OLE pointer held in Uniface. This function must be exported as follows: XEXPORT (void) UOLEINSERTOBJECT (void) Copy If the user focuses on the uOleContainer , by pressing either GOLD D or Control+D, the Detail trigger is activated. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}